 15ŌåÆ/**
 16ŌåÆ * Compliance provider interface and types.
 17ŌåÆ * Constitution Principle V: Pluggable Architecture ŌĆö new providers
 18ŌåÆ * implement ComplianceProvider without modifying orchestration logic.
